      "text": [
        "1186 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «يُجْزِيكَ مِنَ اَلْقِرَاءَةِ إِذَا كُنْتَ مَعَهُمْ مِثْلُ حَدِيثِ اَلنَّفْسِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1186 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"It is sufficient for you to recite like a whisper to yourself when you are with them (in congregation).\""
        ]
      }
    },
